    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ちょっといいー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ can I have a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ前にいいとこ見つけたんだー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I found a great spot before the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "打ち上げまでまだ時間あるし……\nちょっと付き合ってくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s still some time before the afterparty.\nWould you come with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、いいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ no problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "やたっ\n{user}さんありがとー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nThanks‚ {user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、それじゃさっそく行ってみよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No time to waste! Let’s go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
