      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 42.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "えーと、確かこの辺に……あった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ it was around here somewhere… there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 50.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nぽかーんてしてるけどどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!\nWhat’s that dumbfounded look for?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "見ての通り、ドーナツ屋さんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As you can see! It’s a donut shop!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いいとこって……この屋台のことか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you said “great spot”… you meant this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 62.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あぁ、ちがうちがう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? No‚ silly‚ of course not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツを食べながら見たい景色があるんだよねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s something I want to show you‚ while we eat donuts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 68.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "会場に向かう時に見つけた場所でさ\n夜になったら絶対キレイだろうなって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A spot I found on the way to the venue.\nI’m sure it will be fantastic at night!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 75.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "さーて、何を買おうかなー？\nう～ん、どれも美味しそうだなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now then‚ what to buy?\nWow‚ they all look so delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今日は頑張ったからな、ごちそうするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve done well today‚ so this is my treat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 89.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "ほんと？　わーい！\n{user}さんってば太っ腹～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Yay!\nYou’re so generous‚ {user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 95.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ厚意に甘えて……\nここからここまで全部注文しちゃおっかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ if you insist…\nI’ll order everything from here… to here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら\n打ち上げ前なんだからほどほどにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ cool it.\nWe still have the afterparty. Go easy on the donuts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 107.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "ちぇー、残念！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bah! No fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "それならオーソドックスにオールドとチョコと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll go with the standard old-fashioned and chocolate—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 116.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "あ、チュロス！\n最近食べてなかったんだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ a churro!\nI haven’t had one of those recently!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summer_fes-beach",
      "startTime": 120.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_02-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "この月の形したドーナツもかわいいし美味しそう！\n新作だってー、これも食べよーっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That moon-shaped donut is cute and looks delicious!\nOh‚ a new donut? I have to try that too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
